Super excited that Amazon has taken another step forward to a sustainable future! 🕊 

Now when you buy groceries that require refrigeration or cold storage, Amazon Fresh has replaced traditional gel packs with frozen water bottles. 

The bottles are made of PET ( which means that are 100% curbside recyclable ) 

Small steps together multiplied by millions of people can transform the world 🌎 

@amazon.sg #amazonfresh #sp

Amaranthine is a brilliant project created by @suffianhakim 👺 The story revolves around a museum procurement specialist who hunts for artefacts while trying to solve her biggest historical challenge: how and why is she immortal? Meanwhile, sinister elements in the shadows plot to destroy her once and for all before she uncovers a secret that could change our understanding of the nature of humanity forever.

I had a great time filming this inside the Asian civilization museum. With so much history and so many artifacts around me at all times I couldn’t help myself but to check out all of the displays whilst filming. As this is only a pilot with your help and support we can get this project green lit 🔥 and you can find out what happens to Amaranthine 10 episodes down the road 🧛🏼‍♀️

If you have time time help fill out this form and give us some feed back about the show! 

https://mediacorp.votigo.com/fbsignupforms/sweeps/ProjectPremiereSurvey

🎉 Giveaway 🎉

Las Palmas is hands down my new favorite bar in town. Serving up west coast favs such as tacos, baby back ribs, and cocktails inspired by downtown LA… You dont need to fly 15 hours to get a taste of Cali anymore ❤️‍🔥

Follow @laspalmasbarsg and tag a friend in the comments below to stand a chance to win a Las Palmas Discovery Experience for Two, which includes signature cocktails and signature F&B offerings for you and a Palm Springs buddy to enjoy. Good luck! 🎉

@token2049 in the books 📖 What an honor it is to host and be in the same room as some of the greats of Crypto currency and Web 3, and to see their insights into the future of finance. 🏎 🎉 F1 Giveaway 🎉🏎

F1 is finally back in Singapore and I’m super excited about it! 

If your an F1 fan here’s your chance to win 2x *Pit Lane Experience tickets* 29 Sept, 7.30pm onwards, Marina Bay Street Circuit 🚦

Here you will get a sneak peek into the world of Formula 1 with the Pit Lane Experience on The 29th. Lucky fans will be able to view the F1 team garages and cars up close. Experience the F1 village in Zone 1 of the Marina Bay Street Circuit and enjoy performances a day before the circuit park officially opens 🍾

To enter, all you have to do is follow me, tag 3 friends and tell me about your favorite activities to do in Singapore 🇸🇬 

One Lucky winner will be chosen by random! All the best!!! 🏎🏎🏎
